UK money market forecasts 600 mln stg shortage . The average of forecasts by UK money market brokers of Tuesday ' s market shortage is 600 million stg , according to a Reuter market survey . The official forecast for the shortage will be released by the Bank of England at between 0845 GMT and 0900 GMT . Monday ' s final shortage was 700 million stg . - - London Newsroom + 44 171 542 5109 
